<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Audi A8 Guide - Dark Black, Blue, and Violet Theme</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000, #1a1a1a); /* Black gradient */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #fff; /* White text for contrast */
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White shadow */
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #ffffff; /* White */
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #ffffff; /* White */
      display: inline-block;
    }

    p, ul {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #ddd; /* Light grey for readability */
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
      background: #2a2a2a; /* Dark grey */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* White shadow */
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); /* Brighter white shadow on hover */
    }

    /* Images Section */
    .images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .images img {
      max-width: 60%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White shadow */
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Video Section */
    .video-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #2a2a2a; /* Dark grey */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White shadow */
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .video-container:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 5px solid #ffffff; /* White */
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .images img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .video-container iframe {
        height: 250px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Audi A8 Guide </h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Audi A8 is the pinnacle of luxury and innovation in Audi's lineup, offering a perfect blend of cutting-edge technology, exceptional comfort, and dynamic performance. With this flagship sedan exudes sophistication and modernity, making it a standout choice for those who seek the ultimate in automotive excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Single Image Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/664x374/n/cw/ec/37410/a8-l-interior-dashboard.jpeg?q=80" alt="Audi A8 Dark Black, Blue, and Violet Theme">
    </div>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Luxurious Interior:</strong> Premium leather seats with black, blue, and violet stitching, complemented by ambient lighting in matching tones.</li>
        <li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong> Features the latest Audi MMI touch response system, virtual cockpit, and voice control.</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort:</strong> Equipped with massaging seats, four-zone climate control, and a panoramic sunroof.</li>
        <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Offers a range of powerful engines, including hybrid options, for a smooth and dynamic driving experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Comprehensive safety features, including adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and autonomous driving capabilities.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine Options:</strong> Range includes a 3.0-liter V6, 4.0-liter V8, and a plug-in hybrid variant.</li>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> Up to 563 horsepower in the S8 variant.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 8-speed automatic with Quattro all-wheel drive.</li>
        <li><strong>Acceleration:</strong> 0-60 mph in as little as 3.8 seconds (S8 variant).</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> Electronically limited to 155 mph (250 km/h), with higher limits available on certain models.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the Audi A8</h2>
      <iframe
        width="560"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0Vqwnc9twAg" <!-- Replace with a relevant Audi A8 video -->
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>MMI Touch Response:</strong> Dual touchscreens with haptic feedback for intuitive control.</li>
        <li><strong>Virtual Cockpit:</strong> Fully customizable digital instrument cluster .</li>
        <li><strong>Driver Assistance:</strong> Includes adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, and traffic jam assist.</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort Features:</strong> Equipped with massaging seats, advanced climate control, and ambient lighting with customizable colors.</li>
        <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Comprehensive safety features, including airbags, ABS, and stability control.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>